Class Summary

Transaction An object representing a transaction
TransactionContent<KEY,VALUE,RETURN> An object containing logic to execute within a transaction

TransactionCoordinatorManager<KEY,VALUE,RETURN> An object to manage TransactionCoordinators
TransactionManager<KEY,VALUE,RETURN> An object used to easily instruct Transactions
Vault<T> A lock used in Transactions in order to lock resources and modify a temporary value before committing or discarding changes
